{"tid":660134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好冇自信","createTime":"2018-05-10T12:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T17:03:43.000Z","uid":95541,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d9a232d01ce69a2bbf3d16d22947383b2deb03","tid":660134,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"自己好怕醜，成日都因為怕柒，所以唔講野：表達自己。<br />\n例如話喺學校，自己成績都算幾好（聽睇寫）<br />\n但係一到要oral/SBA嗰陣，自己就好似食螺絲咁，講野一舊舊。<br />\n而且喺我六年中學生涯入面，同班上女仔主動講野/被人撩講野的次數唔多過70句/次，近排見返啲同學，個個都話想認識我多啲。<br />\n自己有啲後悔，想作出改變但係又好迷茫，有冇巴打可以畀啲意見拯救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac579d0aff641b6c42046fbfc7e8d6953860017","tid":660134,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4baae53ac0fd8f98b488925e120cc97a43e7b098","tid":660134,"uid":95541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ad927880a3d49a0f9e742521f5ef47083c8ae2f","tid":660134,"uid":95541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>game over</blockquote><br />\n真係咁絕望咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473138e7752c0417a6509e1afb1c3c0726b31054","tid":660134,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f655b627fcc52d6c9536e37b34e62f0882f3256a","tid":660134,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n求救啊"},{"pid":"40d4e86fdb6705f9f1a7056005c54da02ce46937","tid":660134,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84bbcbd7ff1d6b7c5774a423e938bb0867a80e88","tid":660134,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27a46f6b3a4c83a0a09347ea6b